OL,10,FSwiss bank clients to hide their cash
OL,11,Foffered to help the authorities amend
OL,12,Frules in November 2004.
OL,14,FThe law was changed seven months later,
OL,15,Famid an EU clampdown on tax dodging.
OL,17,FBBC Panorama has spoken to the man
OL,18,Fbehind the scheme who claims an Isle of
OL,19,FMan regulator was aware the new law
OL,20,Fwould help tax evaders.
